"2  (1 pound) Bosc pears, peeled and cut into 1/2-inch dice","1/3 cup plus 1 1/2 tablespoons sugar","1 tablespoon all-purpose flour, plus more for dusting","3/4 cup fresh or frozen cranberries","1 pinch of ground cloves","1 pinch of cinnamon","1 pinch of salt","1  package of cold all-butter puff pastry","1  egg, beaten","  Whipped cream or vanilla ice cream, for serving"